{"tid":1610291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知我地爭啲乜？係合作！","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:11:49.000Z","uid":59522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c88ae3e03b488b073f93dfe887f32bcf97613a8","tid":1610291,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"以後現場組5人小隊<br />\n入面一定要有哨兵mon tg同睇水<br />\n其他四人合作推又好整文具又好點都要一齊行<br />\n要有共識小隊點集合，要退到邊先回防<br />\n要記住團結力量係大過一個人太多"},{"pid":"16eda1c74d034c3f4882e765cffa1f671d2f210d","tid":1610291,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/klt1300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fklt1300&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=a59e7f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/klt1300</a><br />\n九龍塘 罷工 集會<br />\n又一城見"},{"pid":"73ef8a778d172bae80b9fff1002a16823c52b71e","tid":1610291,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4168f12e34b074063634791c41d780359cba7264","tid":1610291,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個打機攻略post講過<br />\n<br />\n打機應該要搵5至10個真實認識嘅朋友組隊<br />\n然後按小隊嘅能力同人數, 玩返相應嘅副本<br />\n咁做先係最有效<br />\n<br />\n試諗吓, 1000人, 可以組100個小隊<br />\n每隊都唔使越級挑戰<br />\n只需要做返啲簡單任務<br />\n做完就可以offline抖抖<br />\n休息完再玩過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d64382ab469fc760f9e2bd687e3606cf0e1becbf","tid":1610291,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3c2dec27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d1cf6407494fce3834bc8b07ecb0f6f9d00a20","tid":1610291,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4168f12e34b074063634791c41d780359cba7264","tid":1610291,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個打機攻略post講過<br />\n<br />\n打機應該要搵5至10個真實認識嘅朋友組隊<br />\n然後按小隊嘅能力同人數, 玩返相應嘅副本<br />\n咁做先係最有效<br />\n<br />\n試諗吓, 1000人, 可以組100個小隊<br />\n每隊都唔使越級挑戰<br />\n只需要做返啲簡單任務<br />\n做完就可以offline抖抖<br />\n休息完再玩過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:11:49.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，好過成班唔知想點係度游走"}]}